<li><a href="/wiki/Capitonym" title="Capitonym">capitonym</a>, a word that changes its meaning (and sometimes pronunciation) when it is capitalized</li>
</ul>
<p><a name="References" id="References"></a></p>
<h2><span class="editsection">[<a href="/w/index.php?title=Capitalization&amp;action=edit&amp;section=14" title="Edit section: References">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline">References</span></h2>
<ol class="references">
